# Making a spiral of cones:
open new scene
function ConeStep takes object, color:
	move Object by (1,0,0)
	rotate Object by (30,0,0)
	scale Object by (0.8, 0.8, 0.8)
	set color of Object to (random, random, random)
	end
ConeStep with:
	object MyCone
	color Blue
make a Cone called MyCone with:
	color (255,0,0)
	position (0,0,0)
	scale (2,2,2)
scale MyCone by (1,1,1)
clone MyCone as ConeGroup with:
	iterations  8
	step  ConeStep
save scene as MyScene
